<div style="font-size: inherit;"><ol style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>OKR Software<ul><li>Track percentage-based user acquisition goals</li><li>Monitor renewal rate metrics</li><li>View progress bars for objectives</li><li>Set measurable targets with completion tracking</li></ul></li><li>Performance Management<ul><li>Annual performance review system</li><li>5-point rating scale (e.g., 4.9/5)</li><li>Manager rating system</li><li>Track individual performance scores</li></ul></li><li>Employee Engagement<ul><li>Set follower growth targets</li><li>Track engagement metrics</li><li>Monitor team progress</li></ul></li></ol><h2 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">User Stories</h2><p style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">As a Manager:</p><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>I want to view my team's OKR progress so I can track completion rates</li><li>I want to conduct performance reviews so I can rate team members</li><li>I want to monitor user acquisition metrics so I can measure growth</li></ul><p style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">As an Employee:</p><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>I want to update my OKR status so I can show my progress</li><li>I want to view my performance score so I can track my achievements</li><li>I want to access my review feedback so I can improve</li></ul><p style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">As a User:</p><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>I want to sign in with SSO (Google, Apple, Slack, Microsoft) so I can access the platform</li><li>I want to view help documentation so I can learn the system</li><li>I want to schedule a demo so I can evaluate the platform</li></ul><br></div>
